             was indicted for <rs id="t18170702-46-off258" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18170702-46-off258" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18170702-46-off258" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
               feloniously assaulting 
                     
                        <persName id="t18170702-46-victim409" type="victimName">
                           John 
                           Phipps
                        <interp inst="t18170702-46-victim409" type="surname" value="Phipps"></interp>
